{"tid":586570,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有一種精神叫肥絲大隻","createTime":"2018-03-09T15:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T01:54:29.000Z","uid":111636,"like":68,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3f6bc7580f32b0bb2cd1485f2068c26399e8c548","tid":586570,"uid":111636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"好多人成日鬧肥絲煩，人身攻擊佢，但肥絲面對依啲攻擊佢唔懼怕。肥絲依然堅持自己嘅宗旨，寫好繁體字。<br />\n<br />\n肥絲大隻對繁體字嘅執著比好多鍵國派口講維護本土文化來得實在。每次佢冒住俾人屌老母嘅風險，苦口婆心勸大家寫啱繁體字，為嘅只係保護好屬於大家嘅繁體字，本土文化。佢有做錯咩？我睇唔到。<br />\n<br />\n有一日肥絲都會老，會離大家而去。希望肥絲依份精神可以一路傳承落去，忠於自己，永不放棄。"},{"pid":"f51dddb89e6821ea1c0112e59738d2ef9d776d26","tid":586570,"uid":32298,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"支持肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5811c0b188434333dd56d8fdb844fe0e4f5b3ad","tid":586570,"uid":111636,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"請珍惜肥絲。"},{"pid":"b492279b1b353194f4d678f175874215c2a905f1","tid":586570,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"只有無賴先會賴人哋捉佢哋錯字係洗版<br />\n除咗肥絲玩認真po之後"},{"pid":"d66c47f9b3c5eb12bc266efb4883efeb5e3e4c15","tid":586570,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"有一種堅持叫肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dbcd0d0e1a8a05b5830381111ad144783763e3","tid":586570,"uid":62842,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"我地肥絲精神......"},{"pid":"e68f0c5948a281437214b14c35cb99894ac34c2a","tid":586570,"uid":32583,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:50:59.000Z","msg":"打擊肥絲，人人有責"},{"pid":"f18b3ebaa6da8eb72cfb8a0eac8771a9f24ee6d9","tid":586570,"uid":124140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"肥絲既堅持有時幾黑人憎但又唔可以話錯到離譜"},{"pid":"1d0054ca02d4fea